milestones.description: This is the lowest match aggregate (343) involving teams West Indies & Zimbabwe in ODIs
Iain Butchart has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (6) for ZIM, going past Kevin Curran
Kevin Curran has become the top scorer for ZIM in ODIs with 212 runs, going past Dave Houghton's 176
Kevin Curran and Peter Rawson's 55-run partnership is ZIM's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 41 between Kevin Curran and Peter Rawson
